    "description": "<strong><i>Live streaming is highly encouraged!!</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>One day, Mole Dad ended up chasing his prey too deep and fell into a deep hole, unable to get back out. With only his jet wire on his back, he must fly around the cave using the jet wire and find his way back to his family on the surface.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084360/extras/06ec69bfc1b166cb66dc88ad2d7403b0.poster.avif?t=1723118255\" width=300 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084360/extras/06ec69bfc1b166cb66dc88ad2d7403b0.webm?t=1723118255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084360/extras/06ec69bfc1b166cb66dc88ad2d7403b0.mp4?t=1723118255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>## Controls<br>You can determine the direction to fly using the mouse or analog stick. Press the action button to fly. You can also shoot the wire while in mid-air. If you hit a wall or miss a shot, the impact will throw you off balance.<br><br>## Difficulty Selection<br>- **Stoic Mode**<br>  A mode where you can't go back if you fall. A difficulty level that will challenge avid gamers.<br>- **Normal Mode**<br>  A mode where you can use mid-way saves to undo your mistakes. Recommended for those who are not confident in action games.",
